{
  "title": "Warm Spicy Australian Chicken Skewers",
  "description": "A weeknight Australian dish featuring gochujang and tempering chocolate, this recipe is low-carb-friendly and perfect for a quick dinner. The combination of floral and gooey flavors will leave you wanting more.",
  "cuisine": "Australian",
